Add sshkey to user account when user has a large number of gears

Test machine:
KVM   8GB RAM | 4 VCPU | 80GB Disk
Broker&Node All in one, puddle: 2.1/2014-03-17.2


1.One user, one domain
Create apps, including non-scalable and scalable ruby/python/perl/php, scalable app has 2 gears

Test Results:
36 gears  Add sshkey 1-50
Each sshkey cost about 14s

60 gears  Add sshkey 50-70
Each sshkey cost about 25s

81 gears Add sshkey 71-80
Each sshkey cost about 35s


100 gears(including jenkins server) Add sshkey 81-100
45s

